OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and warm day with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine throughout. The wind will
OL,7,Fstart off light but will pick-up
OL,8,Fslightly from late morning before
OL,9,Feasing once more by the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mild night with cloud
OL,12,Fthickening and outbreaks of patchy
OL,13,Flight rain for some, clearing by dawn.
OL,14,FThe wind easing light in most places.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FA dry start to the weekend
OL,17,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Light winds initially
OL,19,Fwill strengthen during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
